diarrhoea, bleeding,
and exhausting of body fluid,

316
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,920
achieving self-balance of Yin and Yang
will ensure recovery.

317
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,637
What did she mean

318
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,637
