319
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,160
It means

320
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,397
that no matter how sick you are,

321
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,840
as long as you achieve self-balance,

322
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,280
you'll recover.

323
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:14,520
Self-balance?

324
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:21,557
Neiguan belongs to the Jueyin Meridian.

325
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:23,037
Among the Six Meridians,

326
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,280
Jueyin Meridian

327
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:27,040
represents the end of Yin
and the birth of Yang.

328
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,957
Madam Bai

329
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,400
has been sick for quite some time.

330
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:31,637
In the end,

331
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:34,440
we still need to depend on
the Jueyin Meridian to cure her.

332
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,160
She's old.

333
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,520
She already lacked Yang energy.

334
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,517
If you apply pressure
on the Neiguan point,

335
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,440
once the Yang energy rises,

336
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,200
self-balance will be achieved.

337
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,280
