344
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,600
We just expect our body

345
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:04,157
to be 51% healthy.

346
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,480
It's fine as long as health
is the major shareholder.

347
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,800
Both strengths and weaknesses

348
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,040
have their own balance to maintain.

349
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,000
Got it?

350
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:15,960
Understood?

351
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,920
Master, I think

