852
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,757
and the other students.

853
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,240
We hope that the apprentice class

854
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:24,717
can be held smoothly.

855
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,680
Alright, I appreciate that.

856
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:27,080
-Leave it here.
-Okay.

857
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,237
Congratulations.

858
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,077
Congratulations.

859
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,237
Good things come in pairs.

860
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,397
Today's a happy day.

861
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,237
Welcome.

862
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,237
Mr Liu.

863
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,237
May you be blessed with
double happiness.

864
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:37,160
Dad, I'll make a move first.

865
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:38,640
Brat!

866
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,680
How could you leave it here?

867
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:40,880
Come.

868
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,840
Thank you for the flowers.

869
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:45,400
Okay.

870
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,160
How do we use it?

871
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:49,560
I don't know.
I'm trying to figure it out too.

872
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:50,920
Which side is the head?

873
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:52,520
Hey, I'll go deaf, you know?

874
00:35:53,786 --> 00:35:54,717
This is fun.

875
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,720
Are they the same?

876
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,240
Come. I'll help you out.

877
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,840
Look. There's an arrow here.

878
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,600
This confetti is nice.

879
00:36:03,684 --> 00:36:04,678
Let me get one.

880
00:36:04,761 --> 00:36:05,877
What are you two doing?

881
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:06,880
Is there a wedding?

882
00:36:07,080 --> 00:36:08,040
My dear!

883
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,800
What are you doing here?

884
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:12,840
Did you come here alone?

885
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:14,560
Where's Quan?

886
00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:15,997
Hey.

887
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:17,600
It's been a few days
since we last saw him.

888
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,757
Didn't he go to the medical centre

889
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,920
and attend the apprentice class lately?

890
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,677
Before this, we thought

891
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:23,997
the apprentice class would be cancelled.

892
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,640
That's why he was
looking for other jobs.

893
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,797
But I thought he would come back
after the apprentice class

894
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:28,680
has been reopened.

895
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:30,960
Didn't he tell you anything?

896
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:33,320
Oh yeah. He said

897
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:35,157
he's not coming as he has something else
to do this morning.

898
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,120
I'm here to help him apply for leave.

899
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:42,120
How much does this cost?

900
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:47,760
This is great.

901
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,957
Professor, I checked the place out.

902
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,797
It's much better

903
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,080
than my previous place.

904
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:56,280
It's pretty good.

905
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:57,680
It's pretty good.

906
00:36:58,840 --> 00:36:59,720
Professor,

907
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:01,437
you see,

908
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:03,000
I'm still passionate
toward Chinese medicine.

909
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,997
Although the process was excruciating,

910
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:07,280
the end result was fulfilling.

911
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:09,240
I think I'm one of the contributors

912
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:10,477
to the reopening

913
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,560
of our apprentice class, right?

914
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,037
I'll definitely invest in you again

915
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,680
if I make a comeback.

916
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,080
Seems like you resolved
your financial crisis.

917
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,557
Later, we have to talk about

918
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:20,160
how I can make a comeback after this.

919
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:22,760
Let's drop the topic for now.

920
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:23,960
This is a gift

921
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:26,280
for your apprentice class.

922
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,360
Here you go.

923
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:30,717
Hey.

924
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,520
You should at least check it out.

925
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:39,077
I dare not accept this.

926
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:40,480
What? It's gilded.

927
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,357
I got this all the way

928
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,360
from Chokpori.

929
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,677
The Medicine King figure

930
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:46,320
implies

931
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:48,197
that we'll ward off any diseases

932
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,320
and stay safe with him around.

933
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:53,080
If so, I'll thank you on

934
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,437
-everyone's behalf.
-You have to accept it.

935
00:37:55,520 --> 00:37:56,517
-Thank you.
-You have to accept it.

936
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:58,200
-I'll accept it then.
-Sure.

937
00:37:59,160 --> 00:38:00,080
Master!

938
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:01,640
Master.

939
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,440
Look who's here.

940
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:04,837
I made it in time.

941
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,320
This is great.

942
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:08,080
You are?

943
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,480
Don't you recognize me?

944
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,880
I'm Jiang Li.

945
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:12,797
Please pardon me.

946
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:13,920
I cannot recognise people well.

947
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:15,280
I had terminal cancer,

948
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,797
and I only had

949
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:19,560
three months to live.

950
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:21,880
Professor Ren,

951
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:23,600
just be honest with me.

952
00:38:24,080 --> 00:38:26,120
People tell me that if TCM practitioners

953
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:27,520
introduce you

954
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:29,600
to Western doctors,

955
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,960
that means you're terminally ill.

956
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,237
If Western doctors introduce you

957
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,837
to TCM practitioners,

958
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:36,560
that means there's no hope.

959
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:39,120
I'm already prepared.

960
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,560
Look. Even a patient
with terminal cancer

961
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,080
looks healthier than me.

962
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,880
You finally recognised her.

963
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:50,440
I didn't stay idle
last year.

964
00:38:50,720 --> 00:38:52,560
I've travelled and hiked
all kinds of mountains.

965
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,840
I take tens of thousands of steps
each day.

966
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:57,640
It's been one year, right?

967
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,440
Have you been to the hospital?

968
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:00,440
I have.

969
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,120
The cancer is gone.

970
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:05,000
Misdiagnosis isn't that rare
for Western doctors.

971
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,117
Mind your own business.

972
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:09,320
-Can you keep quiet?
-You're wrong.

973
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:12,000
Professor Ren is right.

974
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:14,360
This is karma.

975
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:16,360
I recovered

976
00:39:16,520 --> 00:39:17,360
after paying off my debts.

977
00:39:18,520 --> 00:39:20,437
I guess Buddha forgave you then.

978
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:22,317
Buddha even appeared in my dream

979
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:24,080
and told me that I'd recovered.

980
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,557
Buddha even told me

981
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,720
to pass a message to you, Professor Ren.

982
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,320
Saving a life...

983
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:39,600
Is of boundless beneficence.

984
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,880
My husband wrote this.

985
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:45,400
He is thankful to you.

986
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:48,960
After my family went hiking together,

987
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:50,877
the health of my son and daughter

988
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,040
improved too.

989
00:39:52,600 --> 00:39:54,960
And, our bonds

990
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:56,920
are stronger than ever.

991
00:39:57,560 --> 00:39:58,597
Professor Ren,

992
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:00,320
it's all thanks to you.

993
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:02,760
Excellent writings.

994
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:04,957
Later,

995
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:06,640
you guys can hang it here.

996
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:08,437
When people come in,

997
00:40:08,520 --> 00:40:09,637
they can see it immediately.

998
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:11,440
Isn't it great?
It's your signboard now.

999
00:40:11,640 --> 00:40:12,713
It's our signboard!

1000
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:15,760
Yes.

1001
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:22,240
I'm elated today.

1002
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,480
I wish to thank our kind sponsors,

1003
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:27,920
my master,

1004
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:29,800
his wife,

1005
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,000
and

1006
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:35,320
everyone's favourite teacher,

1007
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:36,640
Ms Song.

1008
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:40,600
I would like to thank
all of you as well.

1009
00:40:41,160 --> 00:40:42,200
Today's the reopening

1010
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:44,280
of our apprentice class.

1011
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:55,520
There's another occasion
worth celebrating today.

1012
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:58,520
I met an old patient of mine,

1013
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,320
which is Madam Jiang Li.

1014
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:04,720
Now,
I would like to invite her

1015
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,040
to give us

1016
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:07,520
an opening speech.

1017
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,320
Everyone, give her a big hand.

